commit.message:
Change v2 schema for parameter.

Parameter now contains a collection of parameter sets which will enable
tracking a number of attributes on a parameter _and_ parameterset basis.
This is because a parameter may be position in one parameter set but not positional in another parameter set.

commit.message:
(AB-1952370) Add link to docs repo in issue picker

Prior to this change the issue picker did not enumerate where to
file documentation issues or requests. This change extends the
list of links for the issue picker to include a direct link to
the documentation repository to file a new issue.
